0:18:45.26,000 --> 0:18:48,000
Spontaneous compassion

434
0:18:48.26,000 --> 0:18:5,000
that could not be planned for,

435
0:18:50.26,000 --> 0:18:53,000
that was unexpected and unpredictable.

